RECODE 
  Herearesomedifferentwaysthatpeoplecanfeelaboutworkingandconcentr
  TO Herearesomedifferentwaysthatpeoplecanfeelaboutworkingandconcen_S
  ('Almost never'=1) ('Sometimes'=2) ('Often'=3) ('Always'=4)
  INTO ATTC_1 TO ATTC_20.

